<title>阿里重大动作，吴泳铭成立电商事业群</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E9%87%8D%E5%A4%A7%E5%8A%A8%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%8C%E5%90%B4%E6%B3%B3%E9%93%AD%E6%88%90%E7%AB%8B%E7%94%B5%E5%95%86%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%9A%E7%BE%A4</link>
